| --------------- | ------ |
| Registration    | ✅      |
| Login           | ✅      |
| Upload PDF      | ✅      |
| OCR             | ✅      |
| OCR Review      | ✅      |
| AI Explanation  | ✅      |
| Save Report     | ✅      |
| History         | ✅      |
