# 👨‍🏫 Mentor's Note

Your Blood Report Analyzer is a healthcare product, so **accuracy matters more than speed**.

One additional practice I'd strongly recommend is creating a **test library**. Collect blood reports from different laboratories (with permission and after removing personal information) and use the same set of reports every time you test a new version of the app. This ensures that future changes don't accidentally break OCR or AI explanations for reports that used to work.

